import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { db } from '../firebase'; import { collection, getDocs, addDoc, deleteDoc, doc } from 'firebase/firestore'; function AdminStudents() { const [students, setStudents] = useState([]); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true); // Fetch students from Firestore useEffect(() => { const fetchStudents = async () => { try { const studentsCollection = collection(db, 'students'); const studentsSnapshot = await getDocs(studentsCollection); const studentsList = studentsSnapshot.docs.map(doc => ({ id: doc.id, ...doc.data() })); setStudents(studentsList); setLoading(false); } catch (error) { console.error("Error fetching students: ", error); setLoading(false); } }; fetchStudents(); }, []); // Delete student function const deleteStudent = async (id) => { try { await deleteDoc(doc(db, 'students', id)); // Remove from state setStudents(students.filter(student => student.id !== id)); } catch (error) { console.error("Error deleting student: ", error); } }; return (
